{"turn_id":8,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T03:14:24.978814+00:00","speaker":"alice","content":"早上好，Bob！咖啡的香气已经飘满整个店了，能给我来一杯热咖啡吗？","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_speech","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":560,"target_npc_id":"bob"}}
{"turn_id":9,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T03:14:48.076882+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"早上好，Alice！欢迎光临。咖啡当然有，我刚煮好的一壶，香气正浓呢。马上给你倒一杯，今天想配点什么？可颂还是松饼？都是早上刚整理好的，新鲜得很。","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_speech","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":560,"target_npc_id":"alice"}}
{"turn_id":10,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T03:14:51.181291+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"已提交动作：speak_to","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_dialogue","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":560}}
{"turn_id":11,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T03:15:00.830046+00:00","speaker":"alice","content":"那可颂吧，刚出炉的可颂配热咖啡，简直是绝配！麻烦你了，Bob。","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_speech","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":570,"target_npc_id":"bob"}}
